ITV Gazza's Tears The Night That Changed Football 576p x264 AC3 MVGroup 2010

The definitive story of the England v West Germany semi-final from Italia 90 - a match that captivated the nation and restored pride in the beautiful game. 20 years on, this documentary recalls the memorable event and features interviews with the players themselves as well as with those who were there to witness it. The programme also includes rarely-seen archive footage from the 1990 World Cup. Featuring Paul Gascoigne, Terry Butcher, David Platt, Peter Shilton, Mark Wright, Des Lynam, Graham Taylor and Mark Austin.
